                        (four in the top of the miniature) and Seven <ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1041HolyMen"/>,
                        including <persName ref="PRS4585Georgeo"/> (bottom left)
                        and <persName ref="PRS4306GabraMa"/> (bottom, second from right)
                        </desc>
                     </decoNote>
